  Tham3-thau5 khoaN3 tui3 chheng5-a2-kha, hit-tin7 lau7-hoe3-a2-pan i2-keng soaN-kou2, chhun Jit8-seng kap Eng5-chin3 ti7 ki5-poaN5 teng2 teh chian3. ¡§A-pa to7-si7 chit-khoan2 lok8-thiong3-seng3, bo5-hoan5 bo5-lo2, chit8-si3-lang5 tai3 chiah8-lok8, iu5-lok8, peng5-iu2 moa2 si3-ke3. Kap Eng5-chin3 tu2 chit8-taN3. Sai-kong-a2 sin5-poe, hi-hi hoa7-hoa7, bo5-kim3 bo5-ki3.¡¨ ¡§Hou5, khoaN3 li2 e7 kaiN5 iah boe7 kaiN5,¡¨ Ui7-tioh8 A-eng, Eng5-chin3 gi2 tai3 siang-koan, chhio3 poah8-to2 chai7-chhng5 e5 Siu3-tin: ¡§Bian2 siuN7 bin5-chhng5 teng2 teh chhia-poah8-peng2--a houN?¡¨ ¡§ChhiuN7 lin2--leh, chiah khoaN3 so2--a2 kha-boe2 that--leh that--leh, koh that chit8-e5 chhut--lai5 koh8?¡¨ Siu3-tin sui-jian5 to2 ti7 peN7-chhng5, oan-na2 m7-niu7 chhui3: ¡§Na7 e7 kaiN5, that chit8-e5 chhit-chap8-leng5 lai5 khoaN3-mai7--leh.¡¨ Goa7-lang5 tai7-khai3 thiaN bo5 in teh kong2 siaN2, A-eng to7 chin chheng-chho2. Goan5-lai5 ti7 i-su-juh cho3 moa2-goeh8 si5, Eng5-chin3 tai7-hoat miau7-lun7: ¡§Tak8-e5 kan-taN houN3-hian5, mng7 goa2 gou7-chap8-hoe3 an2-choaN2 tit-chu2. M7-kiaN lin2 thau-oh8, .... hou7 lin2 so2--a that--chhut-lai5-e5-lah.¡¨
