  ¡§Mai3 khau3--a-lah, toe3 a-peh tng2--lai5-lah.¡¨ A-eng kiu tiam3 Jit8-seng e5 chhiu2-tou2-oan. Bi7-lai5 e5 mia7-un7 chhiuN7 an2-choaN2? Chit8-e5 chap8-hoe3 gin2-a2, si7 gong7-gong7 tam2-tam2. Chin3-cheng5 a-chi2, chit-ma2 a-bu2, chit8-e5 chit8-e5 pang3--leh cho3 in chau2. Bong5-bong5 jin5-hai2, chi2 u7 a-peh hou7 khip8--leh..... Ka-chai3 ti7 i e5 chhiu2-tou2-oan, ti7 i e5 heng-kham2-a2 lai7, A-eng sui5 kam2-siu7 tioh8 un-loan2 koh an-choan5. Sui-jian5 sin-thiam e7 ka7 chhong3-ti7, liah8 chhi-loa5-a2-thang5 ka7 loah. Than3 lang5 bo5 khoaN3--kiN3, han-chi5-khou long2 pheN hou7 chiah8. Kai tong cho3 e5 khang-khoe3, ma7 long2 the hou7 cho3..... M7-koh, Jit8-seng kian3 khoaN3--tioh8, long2 e7 ui7 i.
