  Kui-boe2, Kheng3-tong5 bo5 iong7 ou-thau5-a2 lai5 chai3. ¡§U7 ang-bou2-kiaN5, bo5 ang-bou2-mia5¡¨, soah pian3 siong7 ho2 e5 an-pai5. Sui-jian5 iau2 u7 ui5-ham7, A-eng oan-na2 tit-tioh8 kui-chng-lang5 e5 chiok-hok--lah. ¡§A-eng--a,¡¨ oat chit8-lian3 tng2, Siu3-tin i2-keng khi2-chhng5. ThiaN-tioh8 siaN, A-eng oat jip8-khi3 pang5-keng. ¡§Ia7 bo5-ai3 hoah chit8-siaN, peh khi2-chhng5 chhiu2 khi3 nau2--tioh8 beh an2-choaN2?¡¨ Siok8-gi2 kong2 si7-toa7 e5 kian7-khong, si7 si7-se3 e5 heng7-hok. Chit kui2 ni5, Siu3-tin peh khi2 to2 loh8, chin7-liong7 bo5-ai3 i-lai7 lang5. ¡§Chhai2-giok8 kam2 si7 kong2 kin-a2-jit8 beh tng2--lai5?¡¨ Ia7 m7-chhap A-eng e5 bai5-oan3: ¡§Kau3-boe2-a2 tioh8 e7 ki3-tit khau tng2--lai5, A-hian5 ai3 ke tim7 hou7 chiah8. Bo5, long2 chhi7 kah bai2-bai2--khi3.¡¨ ¡§Goa2 e7 koh ka7 Kheng3-tong5 the5-chheN2--lah, a-i, Eng2-siong5 khah oaN3 beh tng2--lai5 neh.¡¨ ¡§An2-ne siong7 ho2, an2-ne siong7 ho2,¡¨ Siu3-tin hoaN-hi2 kah: ¡§Tian7-oe7 ka7 goa2 kha3-kha3--leh, A-nai ma7 ka7 kio3-kio3--tng2-lai5, kui-ke-hoe2 chin ku2 m7-bat cho3-tin7--a.¡¨ Tai7-khai3 hoaN-hi2 koe3-thau5: ¡§A-nai in hit-e5 kio3 siaN2? Soa3 kio3 chhoa7 tng2--lai5.¡¨ ¡§Kam2 ho2? Chiah peng5-iu2 nia5....¡¨ ¡§A5, kin2--a-lah, kin2--a-lah, soah khoaN3 boe7--chhut? Bo5, ma7 hou7 chai in a-haiN beh thak8 phok-su7.¡¨ Siu3-tin kong2-tioh8 hiau5-pai kah, A-eng ma7 kam2-kak chiaN5 kong-chhai2: ¡§Na7 an2-ne, Eng5-chin3 ti7 goa7-khau2, ma7 chhiaN2 i lai5.¡¨ ¡§I lai5 siong7 ho2, Chhai2-giok8 in ang kap i siong7 u7 oe7 kong2.¡¨ Na2-chhiuN7 hou7 siuN7--tioh8: ¡§Tioh8--lah, ka7 Eng5-chin3 kong2, beh kha3-iu5 nng7-chiah-ke, hou7 Chhai2-giok8 theh8 tng2-khi3 cho3 tan2-lou7.¡¨ Kau-tai3 e5 tai7-chi3, it-it hoat8-loh8 khi3 cho3. Chheng5-a2-kha nng7-lau7 iau2 leh tai7-chian3, chit8-chun7-chun7 loan2-liu5, lau5 koe3 A-eng choan5-sin, lang5 kong2 hok, lok8, siu7 sam-seng-kiong2-chiau3, si7 jin5-seng lan5-tit e5 hok-po3, a-pa, a-i, oan-na2 beh oa2--a-lah. 
